data.description: A tranquil north Dayton retreat, with plenty of space to move, inside and out! Positioned on a sprawling 1.21-acre parcel and boasting breathtaking mountain views, this 2280 sq ft, 3-bed, 2-bath residence is well-maintained and move-in ready.  As you step inside, you'll be greeted by high ceilings that create an airy atmosphere, accentuating the open and inviting layout. The full perimeter foundation and double pane windows ensure lasting durability and energy efficiency, while the sunny interior exudes warmth and comfort. The expansive family room is a true focal point, featuring a wood burning fireplace, oversized windows, and a ceiling fan to maintain comfort year-round. The kitchen boasts a built-in microwave, recessed lighting, a pantry, and an island with additional seating capacity. The adjoining dining room has built-in cabinetry and a set of French doors that open to the covered back patio, creating the perfect setting for outdoor dining and relaxation. The master bedroom provides generous closet space, a large window that frames picturesque views, and an ensuite bathroom with dual sinks, a garden tub, and a separate shower stall. The versatile bonus room that can easily be transformed into an office, game room, home gym, or an additional bedroom. The land surrounding the home is a blank canvas, offering endless possibilities. With RV access and parking, a private well, and a large storage shed, you'll have ample room for all your outdoor needs and hobbies. With its prime location near Six Mile Canyon Rd, Mark Twain Park, and the local community center, this property offers access to a vibrant community. Discover the serenity and space you've been searching for in this charming Dayton home – schedule your showing today!
